Comment: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:05.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}A Typhoon Passes - Illusion and Reality
Comment: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:35.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Setting off - At First Snow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:49.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:03.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's autumn already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.21,0:02:13.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}So, your dad was a tank driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.28,0:02:14.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:16.60,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}He led the escape of over a thousand citizens and soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:22.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}out of the beseiged city of Wardenburg with just six Type-2 Millipads.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:26.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}He's a legendary strategic evacuation hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:28.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:29.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:33.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And my father, who was wounded in battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:37.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}met my mother who was a medic when he was hospitalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:40.38,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And the child they had together was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:43.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:43.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:48.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Hey, I'm not a potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:51.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}My! What a wonderful potato...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:54.57,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's because you cultivated them so well, Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:03:01.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}With these, we'll be able to share some with the townspeople, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:04.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And, Klaus-san is coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:07.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Maybe we'll give him some as souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:08.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Is he coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:12.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You really like Klaus-san, don't you, Kureha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:15.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I-It's not that I adore him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:16.98,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I respect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:17.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Poke. {tsun- onomatopoeia= poke} {Pie: AHAHA- ADORABLE.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:39.73,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Rio-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:44.06,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Wow, she can even do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:46.06,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}How amazing of Rio-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:58.24,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The wind has started to blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:02.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The weather seems to be getting bad, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:04.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Shall we go inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:05.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:05.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:07.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You too, Noel-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:07.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:20.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:23.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Don't you think Rio-senpai is acting strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:24.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:26.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The way she was playing the trumpet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:28.06,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Wasn't that wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:28.83,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:31.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She seems to be depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:34.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's normal for Rio-senpai to keep to herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:36.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But... Oh yeah, dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:39.63,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That tempura was yummy, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:42.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yup! The potatoes were so crispy... {hokuhoku= not soggy. used crispy here fro tempura.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:43.16,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:51.13,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Here you go, Rio. Eat up while it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:53.82,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:58.36,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:04:59.37,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:01.30,Sora no WotoI,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I see. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:07.69,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She munched down the green peppers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:10.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Rio-senpai did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:10.82,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:17.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}No matter how finely chopped they are, Rio-senpai would definitely find them and remove them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:19.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.98,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}...pretty serious, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:32.85,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Poke. {Pie: <3 you, Noel-chan~}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:43.17,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Is this Klaus-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:45.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes! That's my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The Desert Wolf, Miracle Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:52.85,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}On his left breast, symbolizing the unity and glory of the 481st platoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}is a tattoo of a wolf head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:56.85,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Isn't it cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.17,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm not giving it to you though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:04.17,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You don't have to worry that much, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:08.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We were overly anxious about the captain the other time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:15.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Well, it is Rio-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She's cool, attractive and pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:19.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:23.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Even with the peppers, I'm sure she must have overcome eating them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:28.16,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kureha-chan, you really like Rio-senpai, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:31.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She's the person I admire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:34.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I feel the same too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:35.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What do you think, Noel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Poke...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.13,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:58.12,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Noel-chan's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:03.17,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Oh, well. I'll let her have half my bed, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:05.17,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kanata, you grab that end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:06.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:26.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You forgot to put out the light in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:28.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Sorry. That was careless of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:34.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's part of your charm to be decisive and know where to head, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:37.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But lately, there seems to be a shortage of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:39.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:45.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Do you regret hanging up on your father's call?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:50.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It can't be helped, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:54.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'll cover for your errors at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:08:02.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}At least be a cool senpai in front of the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:08.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Is that the wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:11.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Sorry about the late hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.68,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's a Class-1 Priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:17.18,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Who's it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:21.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Master Sergeant Kazumiya Rio of the 1121 Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:26.55,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Please accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:38.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Major, please come in anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:41.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You can't get anywhere in this weather...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:42.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}...not even the Desert Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:46.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I told you not to call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:47.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:51.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}As an apology, how about some hot tea and a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:59.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Thank you for completing your mission in this typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:04.60,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I apologize for serving you leftovers from last night's dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:05.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Please help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:13.24,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You should have woken me up when Klaus-san got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:19.78,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's well made.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's delicious even when cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:23.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The green peppers are well cultivated, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.67,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:27.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I was the one who picked and fried them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:31.74,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kureha will make a great wife someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.08,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Is that a newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:38.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes, the Major brought it along with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:41.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}How are the peace talks?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:44.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The conference doesn't look like it's going to be resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:46.40,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}There doesn't seem to be any agreement on the conditions...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:51.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}If Princess Iliya were still alive, things might have been different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:56.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Princess... Iliya... { Naru: I wanted to cut this line, but we can't because she said Iliya first :(}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:10:00.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You don't know her? She was the hero of Vingt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:04.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The first daughter of Archduke Arcadia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:06.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She's the Helvetian Army's goddess of victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:11.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She's a tank goddess, equal to that of the Desert Wolf Major Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:14.25,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kureha, that's actually-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:16.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Is everyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:17.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}There's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:34.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:35.55,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.32,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:51.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}One of the kids at Yumina's place has been missing all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:52.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Please lend us a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:53.33,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:55.37,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yumina-san, who's missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:00.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's Seiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:14.74,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The river's risen quite high.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:18.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The fields downstream haven't been harvested yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:21.35,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}If the dam breaks, they'll be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:23.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm not familiar with the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:25.10,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm depending on you, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:29.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:32.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}As soon as I took my eyes off him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:35.38,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Search and rescue is an army's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:36.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:44.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:45.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:51.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:52.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Seiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:04.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's dreadful. There's so much water...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}If he falls in...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:15.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:17.16,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Seiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:24.16,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:24.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.80,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You know something, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:33.19,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You came out here because you know something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:35.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:36.69,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Where is Seiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:41.19,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The fields...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:42.78,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The fields?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:45.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Eggplants... are Yumina-oneechan's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:51.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}So, we bought some seedlings with everyone's allowance...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:52.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Seiya must have...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:56.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:22.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:25.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Why are you here during a typhoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:27.40,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I must protect the eggplants!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:28.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:31.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We're risking our lives for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:33.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You came on your own accord, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:35.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I never said I needed help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:37.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:39.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Behave yourself already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:47.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Listen up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:51.18,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kids without parents have to be stronger than other kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:55.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}If you cause any trouble, people wil brush it off as if they had expected it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:13:58.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And not only towards you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:02.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But Yumina, your oneechan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:04.64,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:07.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:11.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm an orphan, too. So I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:15.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Now, let's get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:16.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:19.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Are you still gonna complain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:21.73,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Well, just hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:23.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Things that you work hard at nurturing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:28.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}are as precious as your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:34.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}These are big enough to be eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:38.97,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}So, they'll be really delicious when pickled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:44.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Thanks, Mister
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:46.37,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Major...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:58.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Seiya-kun has started to climb up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Major, please go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:21.64,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}N-No... You go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:24.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Leave the rear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:25.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:56.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The two of them are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:57.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:16:01.19,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Now, their way back up is cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:04.35,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The situation is... disastrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:13.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The situation has become bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But, you're with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:24.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I believe we'll manage, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:28.69,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You're wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:30.76,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Huh? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:32.76,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:39.06,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Listen, don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:42.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You're now with Miracle Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:44.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:46.76,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The ground isn't gonna hold any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:48.76,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Water erosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:52.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Damn! This is why I hate kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:57.68,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kids who don't listen should just be bound and locked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:58.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:01.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What good will come of upsetting them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:06.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Those kids are always watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:10.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm sorry... That was too harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.95,0:17:14.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}B-But I'm sure it'll work out somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:17.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Klaus-san is said to bring miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:18.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:24.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}He's not the Desert Wolf or Miracle Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:29.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}He just happens to have the same name and similar appearance, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:34.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}When they first met, Kureha just assumed and got excited...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:36.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Klaus is a poor talker, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:40.53,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}He just went along with it until he could find the chance to tell her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:42.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:47.73,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Anyway, we need to think of a way to save the both of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:51.33,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}the courier soldier with only long service,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:54.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}and the enthusiastic but inexperienced one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:57.19,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Give them a rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:17:59.35,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}There's no foothold above them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:03.53,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And it's too far to send it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:08.05,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}A way to send them a rope...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:09.85,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Exists!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:14.10,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The first time I met you, Klaus-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:19.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I thought my father would have been like you if he were still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:25.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I speak to others like I knew my dad really well,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:29.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}but it's all gathered from what I've heard from others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.61,0:18:31.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I don't actually know much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:35.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}He died when I was very little.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:36.99,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:04.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Pay attention to the upper left?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:13.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\3c&H0E0032&}Pull! Pull! Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:08.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The Takemikazuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:14.55,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:19.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Noel-chan, how is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:23.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Linear Anchoring Coil online.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:27.76,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Targeting system partial trajectory from B7 to F5.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:28.82,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Commencing alignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:37.32,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:40.32,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Prepare to fire the wire anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:41.82,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kanata, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:42.83,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:54.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:20:00.71,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'll protect you, in your late father's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:06.10,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes... Major...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:09.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:10.60,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:18.17,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:21.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:22.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:32.16,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kureha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:33.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Retract the anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:34.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.18,0:21:05.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Hey, Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:09.12,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We're somehow safe now, so I'll tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.21,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:12.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:15.57,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You are the person I admire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:32.94,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Blue skies after a typhoon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.37,0:21:35.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}So, you wound up pretending the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:37.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Honestly, I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:39.12,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I didn't think you could go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.78,0:21:42.40,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}When I saw the faith in her eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:46.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I got more afraid of shattering her dreams than of dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:50.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That was why I was able to something crazy like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:54.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}In the end, I guess I'm a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:56.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:21:58.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You're wonderful, Klaus-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:01.63,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}isten up, missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.29,0:22:04.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The illusions you make up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.04,0:22:08.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}and what you can feel from the actual person, mostly differ.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:14.17,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Eyes filled with admiration are usually clouded.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:19.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Someday, when you're looked at in that way, you'll understand the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:23.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Won't you at least stay until Kureha-chan wakes up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:26.15,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Can you tell her for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:33.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}...that this is the most honorable wound I've ever received!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.45,0:24:17.14,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.14,0:24:20.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Setting off - Time of First Snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}
